{"ID":"20241011010309-3d9ct8p","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20241011010309-3d9ct8p","title":"剧本版本2","type":"doc","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010526-9fol349","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-9fol349","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"《顾治本：罢工与牺牲》改编版"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-rejggp1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-rejggp1","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"场景设置：中国上海，1927年，夜晚"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-7qz7lep","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-7qz7lep","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"角色列表："}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-dfrtyv3","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-dfrtyv3","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010526-ao697dy","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-ao697dy","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010526-4wwi923","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-4wwi923","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"顾治本：主角，邮政工人领袖，身材魁梧，眼神坚定"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-1pwwdpx","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-1pwwdpx","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010526-r3pqe39","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-r3pqe39","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"邮政工人甲：顾治本的同事，积极分子，年轻热血"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-t3kdzqe","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-t3kdzqe","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010526-xscvruz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-xscvruz","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"邮政工人乙：顾治本的同事，保守派，面容忧虑"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-tjxialm","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-tjxialm","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010526-6xd2s6j","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-6xd2s6j","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"国民党官员：反革命政府代表，身着制服，目光冷酷"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-gfsh1u9","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-gfsh1u9","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010526-g3h4060","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-g3h4060","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"纠察队员：顾治本领导的邮政工人武装队伍成员，身穿简陋的制服，手持武器"}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-zz0pf5r","Type":"NodeListItem","ListData":{"BulletChar":42,"Marker":"Kg=="},"Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-zz0pf5r","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"ID":"20241011010526-38wm3wz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-38wm3wz","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"群众：上海市民，支持革命，表情激动"}]}]}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-z4t4ggx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-z4t4ggx","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"场景一：罢工前夕"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-icww7ym","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-icww7ym","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"(舞台上是上海邮政管理局的办公室，顾治本站在桌子旁边，手持罢工宣言，周围围绕着一群邮政工人，灯光昏暗，气氛紧张)"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-e6kcj8d","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-e6kcj8d","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"顾治本：（声音沉稳有力）同志们，时至今日，我们的苦难已经到了极点。我们被压榨，被剥削，却无处申诉。这份罢工宣言，是我们的呐喊，是我们的斗争！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-a2gzwt1","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-a2gzwt1","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"邮政工人甲：（激动地握紧拳头）顾队长，我们都支持你！我们要争取我们的权益，要让那些剥削者知道，我们不是软弱的羔羊！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-qqdey82","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-qqdey82","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"邮政工人乙：（忧虑地摇头）但这样做真的好吗？我们罢工了，会不会失去工作，连最基本的生活都保障不了？"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-zj5elcx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-zj5elcx","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"顾治本：（目光如炬，声音坚定）恐惧是敌人最喜欢看到的。我们如果连自己的权利都不敢争取，那我们将永远生活在黑暗之中。为了光明，我们必须勇敢地站出来！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-qjahymv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-qjahymv","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"顾治本：（扫视全场，声音更加坚定）记住，同志们，我们是正义的一方，是光明的使者。不要害怕那些腐朽的权力，不要畏惧那些贪婪的眼神。我们的团结就是我们最坚强的武器！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-o6h9nuu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-o6h9nuu","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"邮政工人乙：（眼神逐渐坚定）顾队长，你说得对。我们不能再退缩了。为了我们的家庭，为了我们的未来，我愿意和大家一起奋斗！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-nhnz38c","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-nhnz38c","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"顾治本：（满意地点头）很好，同志们。明天，我们将一起走上街头，向世界宣告我们的决心。让我们一起，为了正义，为了自由，勇敢地战斗！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-2akcssf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-2akcssf","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"(邮政工人们纷纷点头，表情坚定，舞台灯光渐亮，转入下一个场景)"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-sp4li9p","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-sp4li9p","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"场景二：罢工进行时"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-nepkzo4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-nepkzo4","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"(舞台上是上海繁华的街头，顾治本和邮政工人们正在发放传单，拉横幅，喊口号，群众围观，灯光明亮，气氛热烈)"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-3rh10eg","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-3rh10eg","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"顾治本：（高声）工人们的血汗不应被忽视！我们要掌握自己的命运！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-cv04dd2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-cv04dd2","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"邮政工人甲：（向群众发传单）加入我们的行列，一起为公平和正义而斗争！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-to2phgf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-to2phgf","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"群众：（兴奋地接过传单）我们支持你们！打倒压迫者！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-vgnlo5z","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-vgnlo5z","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"(国民党官员带领一队士兵冲进来，企图驱散人群，灯光突然变暗，气氛紧张)"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-9h7qz1r","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-9h7qz1r","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"国民党官员：（大喝）散开！散开！这是非法集会，立即解散！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-l5fz969","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-l5fz969","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"顾治本：（坚定地站在前面，声音响亮）我们只是在和平地争取我们的权利。你们的武力不能吓倒我们！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-ayomfic","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-ayomfic","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"邮政工人甲：（向群众高呼）兄弟姐妹们，加入我们吧！我们的团结就是我们的力量，我们的声音将震撼整个世界！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-tr3e5aa","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-tr3e5aa","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"群众：（回应）为了正义，我们不惧任何挑战！顾治本，我们跟你走！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-8s0695n","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-8s0695n","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"国民党官员：（怒气冲冲）你们这些愚民！你们以为自己能改变什么？立即解散，否则后果自负！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-izyy03q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-izyy03q","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"顾治本：（不屈不挠）我们宁愿站着死，也不愿跪着生！同志们，不要害怕，我们的事业是正义的，历史将证明一切！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-lt4ptmp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-lt4ptmp","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"(纠察队员们挺身而出，保护顾治本和其他工人，舞台灯光逐渐变红，转入下一个场景)"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-pedhzqt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-pedhzqt","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"场景三：英雄的牺牲"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-4waopqf","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-4waopqf","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"(舞台上是刑场，顾治本被绑在刑柱上，面对着观众，身后是凶神恶煞的刽子手，灯光昏暗，气氛凝重)"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-2uo6c7u","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-2uo6c7u","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"顾治本：（镇定地望向观众）生命可以被剥夺，但信念永存。即使我倒下，也会有千千万万的工人站起来，继续这场斗争！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-6m9k6dz","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-6m9k6dz","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"顾治本：（用尽最后的力气）即使我倒下，也请记住，正义的火焰是熄灭不了的。后来者将接过这面旗帜，继续我们未竟的事业！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-ffsrf25","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-ffsrf25","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"邮政工人甲：（泪眼婆娑）顾治本，你是我们的英雄，你的名字将永远铭记在我们心中！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-azxk760","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-azxk760","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"群众：（哭泣着）顾治本烈士，你的牺牲不会白费，我们会继续斗争，直到胜利的那一天！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-xx8vsf7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-xx8vsf7","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"(刽子手举起武器，顾治本闭上眼睛，舞台忽然一片漆黑，一声枪响划破沉寂)"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-qhr2ck2","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-qhr2ck2","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"(黑暗中，顾治本的声音缓缓响起：)"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-ndiwh2b","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-ndiwh2b","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"顾治本：（声音回荡）工人阶级的儿子——中国共产党万岁！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-6pyddf6","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-6pyddf6","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"(舞台逐渐亮起，展现出一片红色的光芒。在光芒中，顾治本的身影虽然消失，但他的精神和信念如同火种，燃烧在每一个观众的心中)"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-0r26ngy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-0r26ngy","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"(群众和邮政工人们走上舞台，围成一个圈，手拉手，面向观众)"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-e0ph019","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-e0ph019","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"邮政工人甲：（激动地）顾治本烈士的精神永远照亮我们前进的道路！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-6tnn1ii","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-6tnn1ii","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"群众：（齐声）为了正义，为了自由，我们将继续斗争！"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-bb5tbbu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-bb5tbbu","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"(所有人齐声高唱，声音嘹亮，充满力量。舞台上方出现“顾治本烈士永垂不朽”的字幕)"}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-hfzu7rc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-hfzu7rc","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"strong","TextMarkTextContent":"尾声："}]},{"ID":"20241011010526-hm314zv","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20241011010526-hm314zv","updated":"20241011010526"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"em","TextMarkTextContent":"(舞台渐暗，只留下红色的光芒和“顾治本烈士永垂不朽”的字幕，直到一切都归于寂静)"}]}]}